name: Frenchie: A Super Fun French Bulldog Flying Adventure
name_original: Frenchie: A Super Fun French Bulldog Flying Adventure
description:
Frenchie: A Super Fun French Bulldog Flying Adventure is an arcade game developed by Huanman studios. It was originally released in 2014. Huanman studios published the game.
Frenchie: A Super Fun French Bulldog Flying Adventure is available on iOS.
